              <li class="plan-feat"><span class="feat-check">✓</span> Team (3 members)</li>
              <li class="plan-feat"><span class="feat-check">✓</span> Priority AI speed</li>
              <li class="plan-feat"><span class="feat-check">✓</span> Startup/freelance paths</li>
